reviews.headline: LOVE this gloss stick!
reviews.comments: I did a mass exodus of all of my expired lip products recently, and I needed something rosy but sheer to replace what I had gotten rid of. I picked up Fenty Glow on a whim and I absolutely LOVE it! It's sheer enough to wear over other lipsticks, but also pigmented and sparkly enough to wear alone. It's very hydrating, too. Overall, I highly recommend this product!

reviews.headline: Flamingo Fling
reviews.comments: It's ok. The Flamingo Fling color has a really strong strawberry smell to it.  The color is a lighter pink than hot pink, and the glitter gives it a frosty look. However the glitter is gritty. I wouldn't repurchase this at this price point.

reviews.headline: would give 6 stars if I could
reviews.comments: I put off buying this because I had so many other lip products, but I eventually caved because of the shade and the glitter. I'm so glad I did because I've been wearing it nonstop. This is absolutely, 100% my perfect lipstick. Fenty Glow is an insanely beautiful shade on my skin tone and the blue sparkles in it really make it special. it also smells AMAZING and feels super moisturizing on my lips. I wish I'd bought this earlier because I don't think I'll ever need another go-to lipstick ever again.

reviews.headline: Nice, shimmery gloss
reviews.comments: The packaging of this Gloss Bomb Stick is sleek and feels nice in the hand, almost like a fancy lipstick. The color payoff is super gorgeous: a deep, glossy brown that looks rich but still wearable. It's hydrating and smooth, not sticky at all. The shine lasts for a few hours before fading, but it wears off evenly. Easy to wear and fun glossy balm.

faceoff_positive.comments:
As a makeup enthusiast, I was thrilled to try the new Confidential Glossy Lipstick with Shimmer, and I must say, it's a delightful addition to my collection. The packaging is sleek and elegant, catching the eye immediately.

Upon application, I was impressed by the creamy texture that glides on effortlessly. The formula feels lightweight and comfortable on the lips, unlike some glossy lipsticks that can feel sticky or heavy. The shimmer is subtle yet noticeable, adding a beautiful dimension to the lips without being overpowering.

The color payoff is impressive, offering a rich, pigmented look with just one swipe. I particularly love the peachy shade, which gives a fresh, youthful appearance perfect for both day and night looks. The glossy finish provides a plumping effect, making my lips appear fuller and more hydrated.

What truly sets this lipstick apart is its longevity. Despite its glossy nature, it manages to stay put for several hours, even through light eating and drinking. The shimmer particles don't migrate, maintaining a polished look throughout wear.

One minor drawback is that it may require touch-ups after a heavy meal, but that's to be expected with most glossy formulations. The hydrating feel on the lips more than makes up for this, as my lips feel nourished even after the color has faded.

Overall, I'd rate this Confidential Glossy Lipstick with Shimmer a solid 4.5 out of 5 stars. It's a versatile product that combines the best of both worlds - the shine of a gloss and the color payoff of a traditional lipstick, with the added bonus of a flattering shimmer. Whether you're a makeup novice or a seasoned beauty lover, this lipstick is definitely worth adding to your makeup bag.
faceoff_positive.headline: Good to have one

faceoff_negative.comments: The packing is very nice n not cheap like some lipsticks it doesn't seem like it would scratch easy as well. Now to the formula there is no fragrance and it glides on the lip and you don't feel the specks on glitter. It doesn't feel grainy on the lip and last about a lil less than an hour it's hydrating but you still need to apply a lip balm before you apply this. The glitter does last a little girl even after the color is gone the lil specks are there on your lip. Not a lot that it would bother me just something to be aware of. Overall it's good but I don't like it for daytime for me I like a lil muted not too much glitter on my lips but it's perfect for the night outs. I'm a gloss girly but not shimmer glosses atleast not anymore I like just a slight pigmented gloss but if you love shimmer glosses this is for you. Also the glitters are silvery/icy types not the glodenly types if that makes sense.
